<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 03:12:10 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国投资者涌向海外 境外投资触及上限</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-investors-rush-abroad-hitting-outbound-investment-limit-2024-03-06/</link><description>中国资金正以极快的速度涌入投资离岸资产的基金，这与境外投资限制相抵触，并使北京方面振兴国内市场和稳定人民币的努力变得更加复杂。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 02:51:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-investors-rush-abroad-hitting-outbound-investment-limit-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪在巴西建设生产基地</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-starts-construction-manufacturing-complex-brazil-2024-03-06/</link><description>中国电动汽车巨头比亚迪周三向路透社证实，该公司已开始在巴西建设生产基地。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 02:44:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-starts-construction-manufacturing-complex-brazil-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国股市引领亚洲走低，金价创历史新高后震荡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-06/</link><description>亚洲股市周三在谨慎交易中走软，其中中国股市下滑，因为北京方面缺乏大规模刺激措施令一些投资者感到失望，而黄金和比特币在触及历史新高后有所回落。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 02:37:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪将其最低价电动汽车海鸥的起价下调5.4%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-lowers-starting-price-its-lowest-priced-ev-model-seagull-by-54-2024-03-06/</link><description>中国电动汽车(EV)巨头比亚迪周三将其最低价电动汽车海鸥新版本的起价比其替代车型降低了5.4%，为全球最大汽车市场激烈的价格战火上浇油。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 01:58:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-lowers-starting-price-its-lowest-priced-ev-model-seagull-by-54-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>由于对中国经济增长的担忧与减产发生冲突，油价小幅下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-fell-slightly-china-growth-worries-clash-with-output-cuts-2024-03-06/</link><description>油价周三小幅下跌，原因是对全球最大原油进口国中国需求增长的担忧与主要产油国减产导致供应紧张的迹象相冲突。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 01:57:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-fell-slightly-china-growth-worries-clash-with-output-cuts-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>南海紧张局势下东盟峰会聚焦海上安全和贸易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asean-summit-focus-maritime-security-trade-amid-south-china-sea-tensions-2024-03-06/</link><description>澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴内斯周三表示，随着北京寻求加强其在有争议的南海的存在，海上安全、贸易和清洁能源将塑造该国与东盟的未来。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 00:23:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/asean-summit-focus-maritime-security-trade-amid-south-china-sea-tensions-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国习近平召唤“新生产力”，但老问题依然存在</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-xi-summons-new-productive-forces-old-questions-linger-economy-2024-03-05/</link><description>面对多年来最严峻的经济挑战，中国领导层已责成各部委和地方政府落实习近平主席的新口号：释放“新生产力”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 23:03:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-xi-summons-new-productive-forces-old-questions-linger-economy-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>早间买盘：风险反弹突然停止</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-03-05/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 21:49:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>参议员卢比奥寻求提高关税以阻止中国“涌入美国汽车市场”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/senator-rubio-seeks-stiffer-tariff-stop-china-flooding-us-auto-markets-2024-03-05/</link><description>美国共和党参议员卢比奥周二提议大幅提高中国汽车进口关税2万美元，以阻止中国“涌入美国汽车市场”，这是华盛顿保护美国汽车制造商和汽车工人的最新举措。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 21:33:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/senator-rubio-seeks-stiffer-tariff-stop-china-flooding-us-auto-markets-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟将允许对中国电动汽车征收追溯关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-set-allow-possible-retroactive-tariffs-chinese-evs-2024-03-05/</link><description>欧盟委员会计划开始对中国电动汽车（EV）进口进行海关登记，这意味着如果欧盟的贸易调查随后得出结论认为它们正在接受不公平补贴，那么从那时起它们可能会受到关税打击。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 21:20:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-set-allow-possible-retroactive-tariffs-chinese-evs-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>比亚迪引领中国电动汽车进军澳大利亚这个更加友好的市场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/byd-spearheads-chinese-electric-car-push-australia-friendlier-market-2024-03-05/</link><description>比亚迪和其他中国汽车制造商正在向澳大利亚大量推出新的电动汽车车型，在澳大利亚市场，他们没有面临贸易壁垒，而且由于电动汽车补贴和税收优惠以及高汽油价格，销量激增。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 21:05:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/byd-spearheads-chinese-electric-car-push-australia-friendlier-market-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>立法者寻求迫使字节跳动剥离 TikTok，否则将面临美国禁令</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/lawmakers-seek-force-bytedance-divest-tiktok-or-face-us-ban-2024-03-05/</link><description>美国两党议员小组周二提出立法，给予中国字节跳动约六个月的时间剥离流行短视频应用 TikTok，否则将面临美国禁令。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 17:14:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/lawmakers-seek-force-bytedance-divest-tiktok-or-face-us-ban-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯称正在考虑与中国合作在月球上建设核电站</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/russia-china-are-considering-putting-nuclear-power-unit-moon-ria-2024-03-05/</link><description>俄罗斯航天局局长尤里·鲍里索夫周二表示，俄罗斯和中国正在考虑从 2033 年至 35 年在月球上建造一座核电站，他表示，有一天可能会允许在月球上建造定居点。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 12:28:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/russia-china-are-considering-putting-nuclear-power-unit-moon-ria-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>法国“蜘蛛侠”攀登塔楼支持菲律宾南海主张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/french-spiderman-scales-tower-support-philippines-south-china-sea-claims-2024-03-05/</link><description>周二，一名被称为“法国蜘蛛侠”的自由攀登者爬上了马尼拉的一座摩天大楼，以支持菲律宾在有争议的南中国海的海洋主张。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 10:36:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/french-spiderman-scales-tower-support-philippines-south-china-sea-claims-2024-03-05/</guid></item><item><title>华为人气飙升，苹果 iPhone 在中国销量暴跌 24%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apples-china-iphone-sales-plunge-24-first-six-weeks-2024-report-says-2024-03-05/</link><description>研究公司 Counterpoint 的数据显示，2024 年前六周，苹果 iPhone 在中国的销量同比下降了 24%，因为这家美国公司面临着来自华为 (HWT.UL) 等国内竞争对手的日益激烈的竞争。</description><pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 07:22:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apples-china-iphone-sales-plunge-24-first-six-weeks-2024-report-says-2024-03-05/</guid></item></channel></rss>